                     <h3>About Course</h3>
						<p>ALLEN CAREER INSTITUTE has established itself as a leader in  the preparation for JEE (Main)/AIEEE. Year after year, it has given the best  results in JEE (Main)/AIEEE. JEE (Main) courses designed by ALLEN are unique  and are as per the latest examination pattern, which train the students to  outperform in JEE (Main) exam. In order to draw the best out of the students  and make them deliver top results, we provide the required guidance to the  students. The JEE (Main) rank is based on the combined score of board exams and  JEE (Main), so we have designed the course structure in a manner that supports  students to perform up to the required standards in boards as well as JEE.  While designing the course, we focus on the theoretical concepts and practical  problems; keeping in mind the changing patterns and trends in the competitive  and school level examination.</p>
						<p> Based on the extensive research and expertise of several  years in the coaching of JEE (Main), the practice material at ALLEN is  developed by our well recognized subject experts. The practice problems are  designed in a structured and scientific way that facilitates the students to  develop a complete understanding. We coach our students from the very grass  root level and this enables them to achieve the best rank in engineering  entrance exams.</p>
						<p>Our classroom sessions for JEE (Main) course are so  interactive that they serve as a perceptive guide since we value the  significance of personal guidance in nurturing young minds to their absolute  potential. We inculcate deep knowledge of the subjects in our students by means  of our holistic approach which aids them in every aspect of life.</p>
						<p>We believe that there is a champion in every student which  needs to be discovered. ALLEN endeavors to discover the hidden champions and so  it brings together the most renowned faculty, the most comprehensive course  material, and the best teaching methodology. Periodic tests at ALLEN are  rigorous and give an actual simulation of JEE (Main) and other top engineering  entrance examinations.</p>
